OL,3,C'Literally the worst timing ever':
OL,4,CHSBC banking services crash amid
OL,5,CBlack Friday frenzy
OL,7,FHSBC Bank has left thousands of its
OL,8,Fcustomers furious after some of its
OL,9,Fservices crashed on Black Friday.
OL,11,FCustomers said they have been unable
OL,12,Fto make card payments online or via
OL,13,Fthe app on what is largely considered
OL,14,Fto be one of the busiest shopping
OL,15,Fdays of the year.
OL,17,FThe bank apologised in a statement,
OL,18,Fsaying the problem was caused by an
OL,19,F"internal systems issue" that started
OL,20,Fshortly before 9am on Friday.
